high_descs: Turn right and go to the right side of the gray table across the kitchen.
Pick up the gray knife from the table.
Go around the table to the front.
Slice the tomato near the white mug.
Turn right and go to the cabinet below counter on the right of the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the cabinet.
Turn around and go back to the gray table.
Pick up one end slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato slice in the refrigerator and take it out.
Go back to the gray table.
Place the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Go to the table.
Pick up the butter knife in front of the lettuce.
Move around the table to the left.
Slice the tomato near the center of the table.
Go to cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Put the butter knife in the cabinet.
Go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the table.
Go to the fridge.
Chill the tomato slice in the fridge.
Turn around and go to the table on the right.
Set the cold tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the far side of the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife off of the table.
Walk to the other side of the table.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Walk over to the cabinet to the left of the oven.
Put the knife in the cabinet.
Walk back to the table by the tomato.
Pick up the slice of tomato.
Walk over to the fridge with the tomato.
Place the tomato in the fridge then take it back out.
Walk back to the original part of the table.
Set the piece of tomato down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of tomato back on the table where the knife originally was.
